    "en": {
      "title": "Sajith asks the government if the position has changed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Sajith Premadasa, the leader of the opposition, asked the government if the stated position of giving the positions of chairmanship of COP and COPA committees to the opposition has changed now.",
        "The leader of the opposition also said that when the current president was working as the prime minister, he announced that the position would be given to the opposition.",
        "He also said that the names of members of Samagi Jana Balavega, Eran Wickramaratne and Kabir Hashim, have been proposed for COP and COPA chairmanships."
      ],
